{
  "texts": [
    "RQ4: How is the Training Overhead ofMSDD-(IA) 3?",
    "OverviewPre-trained LLMs-based SDD methods pose significant resource demands on software development teams.",
    "To reduce the application cost of our method, we incorporate the (IA) 3 strategy during the training process.",
    "In this experiment, we analyze the impact of introducing the (IA) 3 strategy on training costs and detection performance.",
    "ApproachIn this step, we analyze the impact of introducing the (IA) 3 strategy during the training process from three perspectives: trainable parameters, memory usage during the training process, and overall performance."
  ]
}